v0.1.0
- Implemented qfiltr.filter with support for custom test callbacks, regex matching, and string/array contains matching
- Hardened callback handling so missing success/fail/end callbacks no longer crash runtime paths
- Fixed option defaulting to preserve explicit 0 values for limits and queue settings
- Improved queue safety for empty/mutating queue states and per-item timer handling
- Added automated Node.js tests and npm test script

v0.0.5
- Fixed bug in qlimit combo function that was resending the datastore when going into queue mode

v0.0.4
- Added the qlimit combo function

v0.0.3
- Renamed some functions that were mis-typed and the module.exports from qfilter ==> qfiltr
- Working on better documentation

v0.0.2
- Updated README
- Fixed bug in the queue options where global limit wasn't overridden
- Fixed bug in queue that waited the queue length for the initial queue run, which wasn't necessary

v0.0.1
- Initial project version
- A function for filtering
- A function for queueing
